OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FFriends of the Lake District has
OL,8,Flaunched a campaign calling for new
OL,9,Fideas on how to fix the Lake
OL,10,FDistrict's housing crisis.
OL,12,FThe campaign includes the report
OL,13,F"Fairer Housing; Stronger
OL,14,FCommunities", which suggests that the
OL,15,Funavailability and unaffordability of
OL,16,Fhomes in the Lake District National
OL,17,FPark are worsening.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FIt says there is a growing number of
OL,8,Fholiday lets and second homes, and the
OL,9,Fissue is spreading to areas around the
OL,10,FNational Park where workers previously
OL,11,Fmigrated, impacting community services.
OL,13,FThey're calling for better regulation
OL,14,Fof numbers, with changes to planning
OL,15,Frules, some of which Cumbria Tourism
OL,16,Fand the National Park Authority
OL,17,Fsupport. The Government says it's
OL,18,Fconsidering it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FOver the years ITV Border has heard
OL,8,Fshocking stories of people who grew up
OL,9,Fin the Lake District having to move
OL,10,Ftheir families away from their support
OL,11,Fnetwork because they can no longer
OL,12,Fafford to live in the community
OL,13,Fanymore; young workers excited to
OL,14,Fstart their new career after landing
OL,15,Ftheir perfect job, turning it down
OL,16,Fbecause they can't find anywhere to
OL,17,Flive.
OL,19,FEach circumstance is unique but part
OL,20,Fof the same, wider problem: the lack
OL,21,Fof housing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FLeanne Parr, Planning Officer at
OL,8,FFriends of the Lake District, says she
OL,9,Fwas told similar stories whilst
OL,10,Fpreparing the new report.
OL,12,FShe said: "People really struggle to
OL,13,Ffind a house, and when they do find a
OL,14,Fhouse, it's an issue with
OL,15,Faffordability.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Some of those people that we've
OL,8,Fspoken to were firefighters - the
OL,9,Fpeople that have important roles
OL,10,Fwithin the community and they just
OL,11,Fcan't afford to live here anymore. And
OL,12,Fevery other shop will have a 'staff
OL,13,Fwanted' sign in the window."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FFor a long time, workers have often
OL,8,Flived in cheaper areas on the edge of
OL,9,Fthe National Park, such as Kendal,
OL,10,FUlverston and Cockermouth. Holiday
OL,11,Flets are now appearing in these places
OL,12,Fas well. A recent report stated the
OL,13,Fminimum house price in Kendal is
OL,14,F#300,000, putting it out of reach for
OL,15,Fmany workers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FHospitality needs more visitors and
OL,8,Fmore places for them to stay; it also
OL,9,Fneeds workers. So Cumbria Tourism, the
OL,10,FLake District National Park Authority,
OL,11,Fthe councils and other interested
OL,12,Fparties have jointly produced a
OL,13,FDestination Management Plan to try to
OL,14,Faddress it.
OL,16,FIt's calling for some of the things in
OL,17,FFriends of the Lake District's report.
OL,19,FBusiness have answered the problem in
OL,20,Finventive ways, as we have covered in
OL,21,Fthe past on ITV Border.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FLeanne Parr continued: "Some
OL,8,Fbusinesses are actually buying
OL,9,Fproperties now for their staff to live
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,F"There's a further issue as well, in
OL,13,Fterms of climate change at the moment,
OL,14,Fbusinesses are often bussing staff in
OL,15,Fbecause they can't afford to live
OL,16,Fhere. And that's going to increase
OL,17,Fdemand for properties, maybe on less
OL,18,Fsustainable sites."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FOne of the answers has been to build
OL,8,Fmore homes. Westmorland and Furness
OL,9,FCouncil and Cumberland Council have
OL,10,Flots of initiatives to address this.
OL,12,FGeneration Rent has produced an
OL,13,Finteresting report that finds new
OL,14,Fhomes are being built at roughly the
OL,15,Fsame rate as residential homes are
OL,16,Fbeing converted to holiday lets,
OL,17,Fcancelling each other out.
OL,19,FNow Friends of the Lake District says
OL,20,Fregulation, not building, will fix
OL,21,Fthis problem.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F'Fairer Housing; Stronger Communities'
OL,9,FFriends of the Lake District argues
OL,10,Fthat 92% of holiday properties could
OL,11,Fbe permanent residences. Their data is
OL,12,Fbased on official ONS numbers of
OL,13,Funoccupied properties and local
OL,14,Fadvertising.
OL,16,FTheir data scraping exercise found the
OL,17,Fhighest number of unoccupied
OL,18,Fproperties - 35% - in the central Lake
OL,19,FDistrict from North Windermere to
OL,20,FAmbleside and the Langdales.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThese are averages. Individual
OL,8,Fvillages can be much higher. In the
OL,9,Fpast we have covered areas like Chapel
OL,10,FStile and Elterwater having 85% and
OL,11,F75% second homes, respectively. But
OL,12,Fresidents across the national park
OL,13,Freport it as a problem.
OL,15,FFriends of the Lake District argues 20
OL,16,Fto 25% is the threshold at which local
OL,17,Fservices like schools struggle to be
OL,18,Fmaintained.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FLeanne Parr explained: "In parts of
OL,8,Fthe Lake District, up to 70% of
OL,9,Fproperties are holiday homes or second
OL,10,Fhomes. So as a result, we're seeing
OL,11,Fhollowing out of communities; social
OL,12,Fisolation.
OL,14,F"More and more people are on their own
OL,15,Fwithin those communities that were
OL,16,Fonce thriving. Because the population
OL,17,Fis falling, those traditional rural
OL,18,Fskills such as hedge laying, stone
OL,19,Fwall building and so on are being lost.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"There's also a potential risk that
OL,8,Flocal traditions and local dialects
OL,9,Fwill be lost as well."
OL,11,FRegulating holiday lets
OL,13,FWalking down the streets of somewhere
OL,14,Flike Windermere you can see B&B after
OL,15,FB&B sign. But actually, these aren't
OL,16,Fthe ones most people are really
OL,17,Fshouting about.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThey have often been absent from the
OL,8,Fresidential housing market for a long
OL,9,Ftime, are run by people who are firmly
OL,10,Fmembers of that community and have
OL,11,Fthemselves felt aggrieved at perhaps
OL,12,Fpaying more tax than the more recent
OL,13,Fphenomenon.
OL,15,FThe problem people on all sides of
OL,16,Fthis debate have told me they really
OL,17,Fwant addressed is less obvious on the
OL,18,Fstreet. What looks like a residential
OL,19,Fproperty is often a self-catered
OL,20,Fholiday let.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThe number of self-catered properties,
OL,8,Flike AirBnB, has risen sharply since
OL,9,Fthe pandemic. It has also provided new
OL,10,Fways for local residents to rent a
OL,11,Froom and pay increasingly rising bills
OL,12,Fso they can stay living here.
OL,14,FFriends of the Lake District says it's
OL,15,Fat unsustainable levels.
OL,17,FThe hospitality industry has also
OL,18,Fjoined calls for these holidays lets
OL,19,Fto be better regulated.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35816
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FCumbria Tourism argues tourism
OL,8,Fsupports local jobs, communities and
OL,9,Fthe economy. It says visitors stay
OL,10,Flonger in short-term lets so they're
OL,11,Fimportant, particularly for families.
OL,13,FBut, with The Lake District National
OL,14,FPark Authority, they acknowledge
OL,15,Fthere's pressure on housing. They're
OL,16,Fboth part of a Destination Management
OL,17,FPlan that they argue addresses the
OL,18,Fissues raised.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35817
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThey want the Government to accelerate
OL,8,Fplans for registering short-term lets
OL,9,Fand needing planning permission to
OL,10,Fchange a property from residential.
OL,11,FThe Government is looking at it.
OL,13,FFriends of the Lake District wants
OL,14,Fthat and more.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35818
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FLeanne Parr said: "It's not about
OL,8,Fsaying no to holiday lets or second
OL,9,Fhomes. It's about creating a fairer
OL,10,Fhousing market. Then local planning
OL,11,Fauthorities can actually assess the
OL,12,Fimpact and where there are adverse
OL,13,Feffects, licenses can then be revoked.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35819
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Generally, if you're a holiday let,
OL,8,Fyou pay business rates. So there's a
OL,9,Fdisincentive there really for property
OL,10,Fowners to let their homes out as a
OL,11,Flong term residential let. So we'd
OL,12,Flike to see that level playing field
OL,13,Fcreated by requiring holiday lets to
OL,14,Fpay council tax that can then be spent
OL,15,Fon maintaining the community."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G19/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35820
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1774879866
OL,3,CHoliday lets 'hollowing out
OL,4,Ccommunities' in the Lake District, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FSo on both sides of this debate they
OL,8,Fare arguing regulations must change.
OL,9,FFriends of the Lake District is
OL,10,Fparticularly concerned about the
OL,11,Fcommunity and landscape impact and
OL,12,Falso wants tax changes.
OL,14,FWhether those changes happen is for
OL,15,FWestminster to decide.
OL,17,FThe Department for Housing,
OL,18,FCommunities and Local Government has
OL,19,Fnot responded to ITV Border's request
OL,20,Ffor comment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G20/21
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
